&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;it looks like some kind of race condition/bug with umask handling, and has full debug logs on both the client and server, so this might be easier to investigate than the huge mdtest reproducer.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
